    <div class="container">
        <div class="qure__section-header text-center">
            <h2 class="qure__section-heading">Have questions?</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="faq_content">
            <div class="accordion accordion-flush" id="qure_faq-main">
                <div class="accordion-item qure__accordion-item">
                    <button class="accordion-button collapsed qure__accordion-header" type="button"
                        data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#qure_faq-1" aria-expanded="false"
                        aria-controls="qure_faq-1">
                        How quickly will I see results?
                    </button>
                    <div id="qure_faq-1" class="accordion-collapse collapse qure__accordion-content"
                        data-bs-parent="#qure_faq-main">
                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            <p>Most people see improvement within the first weeks of using Qure products, but this
                                can vary. </p>
                            <p>Some Qure products deliver visible results quickly, like smoother, more hydrated skin
                                after your first Micro-Infusion session. For long-term improvements in wrinkles,
                                acne, or hyperpigmentation, we recommend consistent use for at least 4 to 12 weeks.
                                Like any effective routine, results build over time. </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="accordion-item qure__accordion-item">
                    <button class="accordion-button collapsed qure__accordion-header" type="button"
                        data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#qure_faq-2" aria-expanded="false"
                        aria-controls="qure_faq-2">
                        How often can I use Qure treatments?
                    </button>
                    <div id="qure_faq-2" class="accordion-collapse collapse qure__accordion-content"
                        data-bs-parent="#qure_faq-main">
                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            <p>It depends on the product. </p>
                            <p>Most of our products, including our All-In-One Serum and Q-Rejuvalight Pro LED Mask,
                                are gentle and intended for daily use. Our Micro-Infusion treatments are more
                                intensive and should be used less frequently. We recommend using the Micro=Infusion
                                Targeted Eye Patches once per week. and the full Micro-Infusion System once every 2
                                weeks, for the best results.</p>
                            <p>Always follow the usage guidelines for each product and adjust based on how your skin
                                responds.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="accordion-item qure__accordion-item">
                    <button class="accordion-button collapsed qure__accordion-header" type="button"
                        data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#qure_faq-3" aria-expanded="false"
                        aria-controls="qure_faq-3">
                        Can I use multiple Qure products together?
                    </button>
                    <div id="qure_faq-3" class="accordion-collapse collapse qure__accordion-content"
                        data-bs-parent="#qure_faq-main">
                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            <p>Yes, absolutely. Qure products are designed to complement each other as part of a
                                complete routine. </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="accordion-item qure__accordion-item">
                    <button class="accordion-button collapsed qure__accordion-header" type="button"
                        data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#qure_faq-4" aria-expanded="false"
                        aria-controls="qure_faq-4">
                        When can I expect to receive my Qure package?
                    </button>
                    <div id="qure_faq-4" class="accordion-collapse collapse qure__accordion-content"
