                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            <p>We aim to ship your package as quickly as possible. Processing takes 1-3 business
                                days. You’ll receive an email with tracking info once your package ships.</p>
                            <p>Shipping times vary by location but these times are typical per region:</p>
